content: jvelasquez: Opened two refactoring PRs (#4019 and #4018) focused on removing submodules, with PR #4019 specifically targeting "unneeded submodules and workflow" and PR #4018 removing the "characters submodule." Modified 18 files with minimal line changes (+0/-4), primarily affecting configuration files (78%) and tests (11%). Activity was limited to a single day this month.
